description:
`MdtCellProfile`:  This table stores metadata about cell profiles in a radio access network, including identification, location, and versioning information.

`dateTime`: Timestamp of the data record.
`Area_Name`: Name of the geographic area where the cell is located.
`CellId`: Unique identifier for the cell.
`Id2`: Redundant cell identifier (appears to be a duplicate of CellId).
`Id3`:  Ancillary identifier (purpose unclear from sample data).
`Id4`:  Ancillary identifier (purpose unclear from sample data, defaults to 'Default').
`vsDataType`:  Data type identifier.
`vsDataFormatVersion`: Version of the data format.
`MdtCellProfile.userLabel`: User-defined label (currently empty).
`MdtCellProfile.reservedBy`:  Indicates if the profile is reserved (currently empty).
`MdtCellProfile.mdtCellProfileId`:  Identifier for the cell profile (defaults to 'Default').
